N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 79.30 - Loading and unloading of passengers or cargo by vehicles restricted

State Regulations

No vehicle shall load or unload passengers or cargo in or
upon the airport at any place other than those areas designated by the airport
operator. Notes
